# GURPS skill file
# Skill-id ; Name ; Difficulty ; Attribute ; Default ; Modifier ; Bonus ; Prereq ; Flags
#
# Skill-id: unique identifier, one word
# Name: human readable name
# Difficulty: M/E M/A M/H M/VH P/E P/A P/H
# Attribute: Base attribute, ST DX IQ HT
# Default: default of skill, skill-id/+-mod attr/+-mod
# Modifier: which modifiers apply to this skill (comma separated)
# Bonus: what modifier bonus does this skill offer "mod_name/type/#" (comma separated)
#   type can be on of:
#   *,/,+,-: normal math operators by #
#   sdiv: skill divided by #
# Prereq: prerequisites, can be one of:
#   skill/skill-id/#  (skill-id at level #)
#   attr/name/#       (attribute name at #)
#   adv/adv-id/#      (adv-id at level #) 
# Flags: (comma separated)
#   type  (this skill requires a type)
#   TL    (this skill is TL dependant)
# Ref: Reference (book, page, etc)
#
# Skill-id ; Name ; Difficulty ; Attribute ; Default ; Modifier ; Bonus ; Prereq ; Flags ; Ref
